```json
{
  "data": {
    "hero": {
      "name": "R2-D2",
      "appearsIn": [
        "NEWHOPE",
        "EMPIRE",
        "JEDI"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

This `Decoder` type represents a value that knows how to convert a raw JSON response into standard Elm values that can be used in your Elm application.

