```json
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "message": "Cannot query field \"nam\" on type \"Droid\".",
      "locations": [
        {
          "line": 4,
          "column": 5
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

This module defines the GraphQL "error" type, to help parse any validation issues within your Elm application.


